                     RELICS OF DELDRONEYE SOLUTION PART 1
                     ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
                @4   Should take around 13 minutes to complete@3

      Relics is one of my personal favourites from the F1 collection and
      as I have completed it I thought it was a good excuse for an article.
      Anyway the only place I got stuck was when trying to find the "Rhino
      leaf" I had to ask the author and when he told me I kicked myself
      because like everything in Relics it's all so obvious, once you know
      the answer, great stuff. So here we go with the first instalment.
@1
      1) Look at Sheprat. Look at old man. Talk to old man. Use boot on
      Sheprat. Take Sheprat. Give to old man. Answer Please to request.
      Exit through the Magic Staircase.

      2) Open cell door. Go into cell. Take spike stick. Look at it. Leave
      cell. Goto More. Talk to prisoner. Give Spike stick to prisoner
      (he gives you a file). Look at file. Go back to cell. Use File on Poker
      Take Pincers. Use Pincers on Sharp poker. Use handled sharp poker on
      fire. Talk to prisoner. Use handled sharp poker on prisoner. Select
      top hand. and top one again. then middle hand. Take branding iron from
      fire.Goto More. Look at concealed panel near beam. Open panel.
      Look at panel again. Use branding iron on panel. Move to stairway.
      3) Move to central walkway. Go to court area. Answer anything to guard.
      Goto glass building. Take Bananna skin,Purse,pen,card. Goto court area.
      Move to platform below panel. Use banana skin on platform. Open panel.
      Take crystal. Goto walkway. Open circuit box below sign post. Take fuse
      Open panel. Use crystal on panel. Use fuse on panel. Close panel. Use
      Hoverdisk card on panel. Move to Morph bike.
@4
      Well that's the easy part of the game. The next part will take a lot
      of explaining. This part of the game took me a few days to suss out
      but is brilliantly done.
