      Authors comments : Lee Bamber
      Having escaped from the prison complex, you are now a fugitive.  It's
      fortunate the planet is poorly patrolled.  The worst offender of this
      crime is the port town of Zantis, your next destination.Despite the
      lack of police, you will find Zantis unusually clean and free from
      crime.  Working in the shadow of a deadly syndicate, you must charter
      passage from this world and back to your home, Deldronis.  As all port
      towns are places of trade, your best bet is to blend in and play by
      their rules.  Don't forget your hotel card, its value is more than
      its worth.
